TopicTitle: Landing Leg problem on launch pad.

Articles.Content:
I think i found a bug in 1.1.3 experimentals...
Just build a ship with 1 part, add some landing legs, retract the landing legs and, the ship jumps! Poor jebediah

I made a video of the problem.
ps: Sorry for my poor english: Its not my primary language - i still learning how to write in english
